1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
Day three. Time to test the spy.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:06,000
Drop a hint at the well — "she glows at night when she meditates." Watch her.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Sister Cuiwei... my lady meditates every night, and her body... seems to glow.

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:15,000
Glow? ...What color of glow?

5
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:17,000
She must've turned to Buddhism — just chanting.

6
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:22,000
[A fingertip punches the paper window — one eye peers in]

7
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:28,000
Let her see — just not enough. That's how you bait.

8
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:34,000
Her eyes went red looking at you — like a starving wolf on meat!

9
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:41,000
"Health exercises"? Some wandering Taoist taught me. Nothing big.

10
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:47,000
She thinks I'm a mortal who grew demonic power. Tonight, she strikes.

11
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:53,000
My lady, I brought you a midnight bowl. — Midnight? How thoughtful.

12
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:58,000
Let me feed it to you. — So you finally couldn't hold back?

13
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:04,000
You... you're a demon too?!

14
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:11,000
Stronger than Madam Liu. Mid Jade-Rank... that's it?

15
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:18,000
The Empress sent us! One more in the imperial kitchen — "Madam Liu" — the strongest of us three.

16
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:22,000
Lesser demon Cuiwei slain. EXP +10. 195/500.

17
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:25,000
Imperial kitchen... Madam Liu. Time to switch rooms again.
